Package: scTAMsExplorer
Title: Interactive Single-Cell RNA-seq Atlas Explorer
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Francesco Patanè", 
           email = "francesco.patane@ulb.be", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0001-8619-447X"))
Description: A modular Shiny dashboard for exploring single-cell RNA-seq
    atlases built with Seurat. Provides interactive tools for UMAP
    visualisation, differential gene expression, volcano plots, pathway
    enrichment (EnrichR), transcription factor network analysis,
    co-expression module exploration (hdWGCNA), and TF regulon heatmaps.
    Launch the app on any Seurat object with a single function call.
